Yasmine Chouikh (amụrụ n'afọ 1982) bụ onye Algeria na-achụ nta akụkọ na onye nduzi ihe nkiri
Ihe nkiri mbụ ya, ihe nkiri ịhụnanya a kpọrọ Until The End Of Time, meriri ihe nrite Best First Feature na FESPACO 2019.
A mụrụ Yasmine Chouikh na 1982 na Algiers, nwa nwanyị nke onye nduzi ihe nkiri na onye edemede Yamina Bachir na onye na-eme ihe nkiri na-eduzi Mohamed Chouikh
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na nkà mmụta akparamàgwà mmadụ na agụmakwụkwọ
Ọ bụ onye nduzi nka nke Taghit International Short Film Festival.
